e informe o Coronel Eizawa.

00:22:14.160 --> 00:22:15.279
Amanhã à tarde,

00:22:15.640 --> 00:22:16.839
Faremos uma visita a ele.

00:22:17.119 --> 00:22:17.880
Sim, senhor.

00:22:18.200 --> 00:22:18.920
Sasaki.

